snippet.title: I Am Future - Official Cozy Survival Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2023
snippet.description:
In this latest gameplay trailer for I Am Future, check out various features like building a farm, protecting it, and a robot automation system to help you farm and survive in this upcoming action-strategy game. Explore the cozy post-apocalyptic world of I Am Future when the game launches on PC on August 8, 2023. A demo is available on Steam.

#SummerOfGaming
